{"tid":1701351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[國際文宣組一齊預備] Mike Bloomberg 參選係會將中港關係議題帶入總統選戰嘅好機會","createTime":"2019-11-09T04:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T01:17:15.000Z","uid":236171,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9a022d4953a501b30ae94aaf454a0950a2a6cd9c","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"有留意美國選戰新聞，或者留意到 Mike Bloomberg 而家積極考慮做民主黨總統候選人。<br />\n<br />\n佢係咩人？<br />\n1. Bloomberg 新聞創辦人 &amp; CEO<br />\n2. 三屆紐約市長<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要嘅係，佢係支那代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢條友真係好愛<span style=\"color: navy;\"><del>人民幣</del></span>中國<br />\n一直以嚟高調奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係佢幾日前喺清淡節目講嘅嘢<br />\n佢話習近平唔係獨裁者，聆聽人民意願喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲避答關於香港嘅問題添<br />\n(全文後面我會貼翻譯)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=k1fa_k90PW0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk1fa_k90PW0&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOFtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=bd8435cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=k1fa_k90PW0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢一直反侵侵貿易戰，如果選到一定即刻停戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvqjFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvqjFr.jpg&h=85377266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲成立嗰個中國版嘅 World Economic Forum,<br />\n叫 New Economy Forum<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBNj8zn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBNj8zn.jpg&h=adff0356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同不斷為一戴一露辯護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5S0S1j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5S0S1j.jpg&h=f3196dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果佢參選，佢必定會就佢嘅中國關係觀護航。到時美國總統選戰辯論，關於中國同香港政策嘅討論將會大量增加。<br />\n<br />\n因為佢嘅對手，無論係華倫定侵侵，都會以對華強硬作為賣點。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候就需要大家不斷 Retweet 同評論雙方嘅論點論據，等香港議題可以喺美國繼續升溫。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"2c0d70180c6a3a245008c96ab5775eb7890003c9","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"節目內容翻譯:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有咩辦法令中、印等國合作減低碳排放？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>Bloomberg: </strong></span>中國做咗好多嘢架（無視印度）。雖然佢哋用燃煤發電，但係佢哋將發電廠搬離城市，減少空氣污染（喂，冇解決過碳排放問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中共為咗繼續當權，佢哋非常原意聆聽民意</span></strong>（吓，我有冇聽錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">習近平唔係一個獨裁者</span></strong>。當人民話好難抖氣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>習近平要回應選佢出嚟嘅人（人大）嘅意見</strong></span>，唔係佢難以繼續掌權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">吓你覺得習近平唔係獨裁者？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔使投票，無人選佢。唯一要驚嘅係咪得全國革命呢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong> Bloomberg:</strong></span>中國唔會有革命架喇。冇一個國家政府喺得唔到全國大部分人支持下係可以持續掌權嘅，OK? 唔聽民意你估佢哋想變蘇聯咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">你覺得聆聽人民對新鮮空氣嘅意願就係民主？咁香港呢？佢哋遊行咗咁耐中共有冇聽過佢哋民意？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong> Bloomberg:</strong></span> 無視香港問題，繼續講北京點回應本土空氣污染問題（冇講過減少碳排放）。廢話一堆，唔翻譯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11b417dcab0d99f2b2a8b631766d82525a2d110","tid":1701351,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"063c6eac69a6a2295b823bdd081624bd79b58777","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"所以呢個時候，襯選戰未正式開始，<br />\n我哋要把握時間盡快跟貼美國政治生態<br />\n知道唔同人嘅政策取態"},{"pid":"26154d3f9c4f0992ef8dd149fae47067e133e648","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"920bcfdafaf711d1ecc581e39240a8bb74811b5a","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26154d3f9c4f0992ef8dd149fae47067e133e648","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"e6a89c2842eaab2db59b923ff94413a141b52c90","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"063c6eac69a6a2295b823bdd081624bd79b58777","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"所以呢個時候，襯選戰未正式開始，<br />\n我哋要把握時間盡快跟貼美國政治生態<br />\n知道唔同人嘅政策取態"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最重要係，要知咩講得咩唔講得。<br />\n<br />\n理論上作為外人我哋係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該</span>評論外國選舉同黨派之爭嘅，呢點之前都有巴打提出過。<br />\n<br />\n但係當議題涉及美中、美港關係同政策，我哋就有原因去講嘢，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為我哋係 stakeholders</span>.<br />\n<br />\n大家要知條界線喺邊。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5466467339d212d29ac7c37b7c93733bae2d534c","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"58a447fb27cf7bbe6aa5151c4e2f02bfc88fdb4b","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b886d874ff66b25beb28da55e7ce26c96c9b3348","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"b2af2d1010c37a125f3d24f872211de162747091","tid":1701351,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06885ce9592663535ff896b07cb43d030672ee17","tid":1701351,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b8c8148a5a5cf9b76f3160a4d8135aafcfec64d","tid":1701351,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ced82eaef8c6f3791850ef279b69c2022bf604b","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5bfea81cd8b9357027050b6a3aa33677409c2bc8","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"dcd59e8a9ab1ba234c32539bc186a60060270e6c","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"632fc2fb685eaf03a0ec3f13a4c375d97decd7de","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"f0a6f8b5d151341a503dce5a94c4a478df089e9e","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"好難推，幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cd9463e2757ea11306fff97431e9c19d83e092","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0a6f8b5d151341a503dce5a94c4a478df089e9e","tid":1701351,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"好難推，幫下手<img src=\"/assets/f